[00:23.46] With life just begun, my sleeping new son
[00:28.82] Has eyes that roll back in his head
[00:33.39] They flutter and dart, he slows down his heart
[00:40.33] And pictures a world past his bed
[00:56.83] 
[00:44.85] It's hard to believe
[00:51.14] As I watch you breathe
[00:59.28] Your mind drifts and weaves
[01:12.78] 
[01:05.54] When you dream,
[01:08.32] What do you dream about?
[01:20.32] 
