[01:31.10] 
[01:29.08] Do you dream about
[01:30.87] Music or mathematics
[01:35.32] Or planets too far for the eye?
[01:50.82] 
[01:40.83] Do you dream about
[01:43.52] Jesus or quantum mechanics
[01:47.11] Or angels who sing lullabies?
[02:01.61] 
